	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106564419125695798">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://search.ft.com/search/article.html?id=031008000791">FT.com | Working out what IT all means</a>.&nbsp; Linked by ACM Technet, this David Bowen article looks at what the Oxford Internet Institute (OII) is taking on as part of Wiliam Dutton's stewardship.&nbsp; There are some great anecdotes about examination of the social impacts of technology and the internet specifically.&nbsp; The Financial Times tends to require registration, so I don't know how accessible this article will remain.<br>
