	<div class="posts">
	<a name="106564275062419930">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.downes.ca/">Stephen's Web ~ Knowledge ~ Learning ~ Community</a>.&nbsp; Stephen Downes has another article in ACM Ubiquity.&nbsp; This one is about treating knowledge as an artifact, something I am not that comfortable with.&nbsp; So it would be useful to look more closely and also find a place to discuss some of this.&nbsp; And I see that there is much more material and organization here than I remember from my last visit.<br>
