	<a href="http://www.javalobby.org/thread.jsp?forum=17&thread=9029">Forums - precisefloating 0.1</a>.&nbsp; Here's some material that I should digest for work on Java Inside-Out because I want to provide a serious look at arithmetic in Java and how that works or doesn't in different computing situations.&nbsp; This site is also interesting and I need to remember it.<br>
